title: Live From “Just for Laughs” Montreal (feat. Brad Williams, Jimmy Carr, Guy Branum, Rich Vos & Pete Correale)
description: Brad Williams is in studio as Jay tells the gang about working on the new J.Lo movie “Hustlers” (not Blade 4). Jimmy Carr body shames the comedy community, Guy Branum & Rich Vos discuss intimacy differences in make out sessions and Pete Correale stops by and gives DJ Lou an ultimatum.
author: podcasts@siriusxm.com (Comedy Central)
